of bad decisions.

00:15.754 --> 00:17.321
[Shouts]

00:17.539 --> 00:19.323
♪

00:19.497 --> 00:20.890
We've been waiting for you.
You're the messenger.

00:21.064 --> 00:23.153
Paris,
that's a straight shot.

00:23.153 --> 00:24.937
Genet:
The whole endeavor scuttled.
Because of one American?

00:25.068 --> 00:26.678
[Codron speaking French]

00:26.852 --> 00:28.854
Most of the city
is under the control of Genet.

00:28.985 --> 00:30.073
[Codron speaking French]

00:30.247 --> 00:31.944
[Speaking French]

00:32.075 --> 00:33.511
Isabelle: The Guerrier are
overtaking the city.

00:33.685 --> 00:35.644
