♪

01:53.939 --> 01:55.506
You miss him, huh?

01:55.506 --> 01:57.465
Père Jean?

01:57.465 --> 01:59.075
♪

01:59.162 --> 02:01.338
Yeah,
but I like it here.

02:01.338 --> 02:03.384
♪

02:03.514 --> 02:05.473
