to seek it out.

05:17.404 --> 05:19.493
I hope you'’ll
find yours here, too.

05:21.930 --> 05:33.985
♪

05:34.072 --> 05:35.726
[Door closes]

05:35.813 --> 05:47.434
♪

05:47.521 --> 05:49.784
[Indistinct conversations]

05:49.784 --> 05:53.222
♪

05:53.222 --> 05:55.398
